{"__ud_title":"建立自己的“开源大脑” repo git for AI","__ud_tags":["Tools","ai","aiskills"],"__ud_update_time":1772590307288,"__ud_create_time":1772590305645,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"建立自己的“开源大脑” repo git for AI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"为了解决在使用 AI 时反复输入背景信息、数据分散在不同平台的低效问题，构建了一个基于本地 Git 仓库的纯文本知识库——"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"AIStudio"},{"type":"text","text":"。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"核心观点与做法："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Git 作为协作协议"},{"type":"text","text":"：放弃封闭的云端笔记软件，改用 Git 仓库管理知识。因为现在的 AI 具备读取整个工作区的能力，通过 Git 仓库，AI 能直接获取完整上下文，甚至通过 Agent 自主提交产出。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"工程化目录结构"},{"type":"text","text":"：建立了一套标准化的目录（如 Inbox、ContentFactory、System、Product 等），分别管理灵感、内容生产流水线、SOP 与提示词库、产品开发等，且目录结构可随需求自然生长。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“大脑库”与“外挂系统”分离"},{"type":"text","text":"：为了避免 Git 仓库臃肿，仓库内只保留信息密度高的文档（架构、思路、SOP）；而体积大的代码项目或多媒体素材则存放在外部独立仓库，仅在主仓库中保留链接和说明文档。主仓库作为指挥中心，外挂系统作为执行单元。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通过这种方式建立了一个可迁移、永久保存的“外脑”，实现了人与 AI 的高效协作。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"Step-by-Step-Guide-实操指南"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step by Step Guide (实操指南)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"建立自己的“开源大脑”，请按以下步骤操作："}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第一步搭建基础设施"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第一步：搭建基础设施"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"创建 Git 仓库"},{"type":"text","text":"：在本地新建一个 Git 仓库（命名为 AIStudio 或 MyBrain）。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"放弃炫酷笔记软件"},{"type":"text","text":"：决定将核心知识沉淀转移到本地纯文本文件中，确保 AI 可以直接读取。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第二步构建目录骨架"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第二步：构建目录骨架"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在仓库根目录下创建以下基础文件夹（可根据个人需求微调）："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Inbox"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Thinking"},{"type":"text","text":"：存放碎片化灵感和日常深度思考。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"ContentFactory"},{"type":"text","text":"：建立内容生产线。"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"子目录建议："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Ideas"},{"type":"text","text":"（选题库）、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Pipeline"},{"type":"text","text":"（发布流程）、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Scripts"},{"type":"text","text":"（脚本）。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"System"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"（核心大脑皮层）"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"存放 SOP（标准作业程序）。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"存放工作流模板。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"重点"},{"type":"text","text":"：创建 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"PromptHub"},{"type":"text","text":" 目录，专门存放给 AI 看的设定和提示词。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Product"},{"type":"text","text":"：产品化内容跟踪与专题输出。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Automation"},{"type":"text","text":"：存放自动化脚本和工作流日志。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Admin"},{"type":"text","text":"：管理账号信息、工具列表、环境配置等。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第三步迁移与填充内容"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第三步：迁移与填充内容"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"输入背景信息"},{"type":"text","text":"：将你以前需要反复告诉 AI 的信息（“我是谁”、“项目规范”、“写作风格”）整理成 Markdown 文件，放入 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"System"},{"type":"text","text":" 目录。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"整理现有资产"},{"type":"text","text":"：将散落在各处的笔记、文档迁移到对应目录。不需要追求完美分类，先放进去，后续让 AI 帮忙整理。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第四步实施中枢外挂策略"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第四步：实施“中枢+外挂”策略"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"处理大文件或独立项目时，遵循以下原则："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"主仓库（中枢）"},{"type":"text","text":"：只放文档。例如：架构设计图、需求文档、README、复盘笔记。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"外部项目（外挂）"},{"type":"text","text":"：对于大型代码库、视频素材等，单独建立仓库或存储。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"建立链接"},{"type":"text","text":"：在主仓库的相关目录中，通过文档或 README 链接到这些外部仓库。确保 AI 读取主仓库时，能看到“地图”，知道去哪里找重资产。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第五步建立协作习惯"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第五步：建立协作习惯"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"日常 Commit"},{"type":"text","text":"：每当有新想法、跑通新流程或项目有更新时，务必 Commit 到仓库。这不仅是备份，更是为了让 AI 获取最新上下文。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"唤醒 AI"},{"type":"text","text":"：在本地 IDE 或支持读取工作区的 AI 工具中打开该目录。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"指令交互"},{"type":"text","text":"：告诉 AI：“读取当前工作区，根据 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"System"},{"type":"text","text":" 里的规范执行……” 你不再需要每次重复输入背景信息。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"第六步迭代优化"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"第六步：迭代优化"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"不要试图一次性设计完美结构，让目录随着使用自然生长。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"定期让 AI 根据现有内容整理目录结构或优化 SOP。"}]}]}]}]}